3#ifndef __NVKM_BUS_HWSQ_H__
4#define __NVKM_BUS_HWSQ_H__
5#include <subdev/bus.h>
6
7struct hwsq {
8 struct nvkm_subdev *subdev;
9 struct nvkm_hwsq *hwsq;
10 int sequence;
11};
12
13struct hwsq_reg {
14 int sequence;
15 bool force;
16 u32 addr;
17 u32 stride; /* in bytes */
18 u32 mask;
19 u32 data;
20};
21
22static inline struct hwsq_reg
23hwsq_stride(u32 addr, u32 stride, u32 mask)
24{
25 return (struct hwsq_reg) {
26 .sequence = 0,
27 .force = 0,
28 .addr = addr,
29 .stride = stride,
30 .mask = mask,
31 .data = 0xdeadbeef,
32 };
33}
34
35static inline struct hwsq_reg
36hwsq_reg2(u32 addr1, u32 addr2)
37{
38 return (struct hwsq_reg) {
39 .sequence = 0,
40 .force = 0,
41 .addr = addr1,
42 .stride = addr2 - addr1,
43 .mask = 0x3,
44 .data = 0xdeadbeef,
45 };
46}
47
48static inline struct hwsq_reg
49hwsq_reg(u32 addr)
50{
51 return (struct hwsq_reg) {
52 .sequence = 0,
53 .force = 0,
54 .addr = addr,
55 .stride = 0,
56 .mask = 0x1,
57 .data = 0xdeadbeef,
58 };
59}
60
61static inline int
62hwsq_init(struct hwsq *ram, struct nvkm_subdev *subdev)
63{
64 int ret;
65
66 ret = nvkm_hwsq_init(subdev, &ram->hwsq);
67 if (ret)
68 return ret;
69
70 ram->sequence++;
71 ram->subdev = subdev;
72 return 0;
73}
74
75static inline int
76hwsq_exec(struct hwsq *ram, bool exec)
77{
78 int ret = 0;
79 if (ram->subdev) {
80 ret = nvkm_hwsq_fini(&ram->hwsq, exec);
81 ram->subdev = NULL;
82 }
83 return ret;
84}
85
86static inline u32
87hwsq_rd32(struct hwsq *ram, struct hwsq_reg *reg)
88{
89 struct nvkm_device *device = ram->subdev->device;
90 if (reg->sequence != ram->sequence)
91 reg->data = nvkm_rd32(device, reg->addr);
92 return reg->data;
93}
94
95static inline void
96hwsq_wr32(struct hwsq *ram, struct hwsq_reg *reg, u32 data)
97{
98 u32 mask, off = 0;
99
100 reg->sequence = ram->sequence;
101 reg->data = data;
102
103 for (mask = reg->mask; mask > 0; mask = (mask & ~1) >> 1) {
104 if (mask & 1)
105 nvkm_hwsq_wr32(ram->hwsq, reg->addr+off, reg->data);
106
107 off += reg->stride;
108 }
109}
110
111static inline void
112hwsq_nuke(struct hwsq *ram, struct hwsq_reg *reg)
113{
114 reg->force = true;
115}
116
117static inline u32
118hwsq_mask(struct hwsq *ram, struct hwsq_reg *reg, u32 mask, u32 data)
119{
120 u32 temp = hwsq_rd32(ram, reg);
121 if (temp != ((temp & ~mask) | data) || reg->force)
122 hwsq_wr32(ram, reg, (temp & ~mask) | data);
123 return temp;
124}
125
126static inline void
127hwsq_setf(struct hwsq *ram, u8 flag, int data)
128{
129 nvkm_hwsq_setf(ram->hwsq, flag, data);
130}
131
132static inline void
133hwsq_wait(struct hwsq *ram, u8 flag, u8 data)
134{
135 nvkm_hwsq_wait(ram->hwsq, flag, data);
136}
137
138static inline void
139hwsq_wait_vblank(struct hwsq *ram)
140{
141 nvkm_hwsq_wait_vblank(ram->hwsq);
142}
143
144static inline void
145hwsq_nsec(struct hwsq *ram, u32 nsec)
146{
147 nvkm_hwsq_nsec(ram->hwsq, nsec);
148}
149#endif
